{"tid":2030191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線歷史老師希望各位幫手CLS","createTime":"2020-05-22T15:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T15:19:20.000Z","uid":34456,"like":101,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"f877cdb2b12a3ae8f2d4d3c60432eb165d202ec9","tid":2030191,"uid":34456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"各位連登巴打絲打！！！<br />\n有兩位前線歷史老師冒住比人炒既危險拍左條片，希望大家可以幫手CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NtD9brZRXFY \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNtD9brZRXFY%20&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=971db77c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NtD9brZRXFY </a><br />\n<br />\n我們是兩位現職中學歷史科教師。就近日考評局取消DSE歷史科卷一試題2(c)一事上，正反雙方多日來一直爭辯不休，為讓公眾能深切地了解從歷史科教師角度對題目的看法，我們自行拍攝一段影片去解說有關爭議。由於拍攝及剪接需時，考評局於今日稍早時段，即在考試後的短短一星期內，便宣布取消試題，漠視一眾持份者，包括歷史科考生及教師的感受。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，歷史仍然會紀錄一切，我們仍然希望 貴媒體可以轉載以下片段，在白色恐怖和打壓愈來愈嚴重的環境下，讓身處於教育體制內、人微言輕的教師，可以為一眾考生及大眾發一次聲，能更詳細地了解作為暴風眼中心的考生與教師的實際看法。<br />\n<br />\n兩位歷史科教師<br />\n<br />\n二零二零年五月廿二日"},{"pid":"f0975f37d36a149dbecd93646bcd093202acd8f0","tid":2030191,"uid":55958,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:18:20.000Z","msg":"好正，好清晰<br />\n不過仆街港共政府已經取消左條題目<br />\n屌那星"},{"pid":"faff7c73373de04aa6a10599f1f7c884ed8e38e5","tid":2030191,"uid":349945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5102635024b7722716943214df4ce8d290fc770","tid":2030191,"uid":30836,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NtD9brZRXFY\" data-sr-url=\"https: